WEBVTT

1
01:17:21.780 --> 01:17:23.470 
但是我没错
But I wasn't wrong.

2
01:17:23.550 --> 01:17:25.480 
他不是我儿子 我的亲生骨肉仍杳无音信
He's not my son. My son is still missing.

3
01:17:25.550 --> 01:17:28.240 
Collins夫人 你情绪很激动
Mrs. Collins, you're becoming agitated.

4
01:17:28.320 --> 01:17:32.380 
是的 我 是    我不要签字 因为他不是我儿子!
Yes, I'm, yes... I'm not signing that, because he's not my son!

5
01:17:32.460 --> 01:17:33.480 
护理员!
Orderly!

6
01:17:33.560 --> 01:17:34.960 
他不是我儿子! 护理员!
He's not my son! Orderly!

7
01:17:35.020 --> 01:17:36.420 
我儿子失踪了!
My son is missing!

8
01:17:36.490 --> 01:17:38.980 
这位病人情绪异常激动! 不! 我儿子失踪了!
The patient is becoming hysterical! No! My son is missing!

9
01:17:39.060 --> 01:17:40.320 
照顾一下 她真的需要镇静
See to it she is sedated properly.

10
01:17:40.400 --> 01:17:42.390 
带她出去 不! 不! 不!
Get her out of here. No! No! No!

11
01:17:42.470 --> 01:17:43.860 
下一个! 不!
Next! No!

12
01:17:44.230 --> 01:17:46.390 
不 不! 护理员 抓住她
No, no! NURSE: Orderly, hold on.

